        "Target": "\u30CA\u30EB\u30AC\u30AF\u30EB\u30AC\uFF11\u982D\u3068\u30B8\u30E5\u30E9\u30C8\u30C9\u30B9\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Do It for the Dango!",
        "Client": "Yomogi the Chef",
        "Description": "Grrrr! Stupid. Monsters. Everywhere!\r\nWhy won\u0027t they leave me alone? I go\r\nto one fishing spot\u2014Monster. I go to\r\na different spot\u2014ANOTHER MONSTER.\r\nWhy are they so rude!? Can you go let\r\nthose meanies know just how mad I am!?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Nargacuga and a Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Au nom des dango !",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "Grrr ! Ces fichus monstres veulent\r\npas me l\u00E2cher, bon sang ! Partout\r\no\u00F9 je vais p\u00EAcher, ils me suivent !\r\nQuelqu\u0027un doit leur apprendre\r\nla politesse, alors s\u0027il te pla\u00EEt,\r\nva leur donner une bonne le\u00E7on\r\npour moi !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Nargacuga et un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "In nome dei dango!",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "Grrrr. Stupidi mostri! Sono\r\novunque! Perch\u00E9 non mi\r\nlasciano stare? Vado a pesca\r\nin un posto ed ecco un mostro.\r\nVado altrove e ne spunta un\r\naltro. Puoi far sapere a quei\r\ncattivoni che sono furiosa?!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Nargacuga e un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Tu es f\u00FCr die Dango!",
        "Client": "Yomogi die K\u00F6chin",
        "Description": "Grrr! Bl\u00F6de. Monster. \u00DCberall! Warum\r\nlassen die mich nicht in Ruhe? Ich gehe\r\nzur einen Angelstelle: Monster. Ich gehe\r\nzur N\u00E4chsten: NOCH EIN MONSTER. Was\r\nsind die denn so ungehobelt?! Kannst du\r\nden Fieslingen von mir ausrichten, wie\r\nsauer ich bin?!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Nargacuga und\r\neinen Jyuratodus.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00A1Hazlo por los dango!",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "Fui al bosque a pescar mi\r\nalmuerzo, \u00A1pero nooo! \u00A1Alguien\r\nten\u00EDa que lanzar fango justo\r\ncuando picaban, \u00BFeh?! \u00BFPuedes\r\ndarle una lecci\u00F3n al gamberro\r\nque arruin\u00F3 mi captura? \u00A1Que\r\nvea lo enfadada que estoy!",
        "Target": "Caza un Nargacuga y un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0414\u0435\u043B\u0430\u0439 \u044D\u0442\u043E \u0440\u0430\u0434\u0438 \u0434\u0430\u043D\u0433\u043E!",
